text: Agnete Seidelin (5 November 1874 - 4 June 1956), also credited as Agnete Seidelin-Raunkiaer was a Danish botanist noted for her study of freshwater plants. She was married to Danish botanist Christen C. Raunkiær. ==Works== * Seidelin, A. (1909) 5. Hippuridaceae, Halorrhagidaceae and Callitrichaceae, in The Structure and Biology of Arctic Flowering Plants, p. 295-332. * Seidelin, A. (1912) Vegetationen i nogle Vandhuller i Nordvendsyssel.
